  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为HealthTech系统画一张完整的诊断数据流图。核心是从LabAnalyzer推送原始检测数据开始，经过DiagnosticEngine处理，最终同步到EMR和HIPAA Vault。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。LabAnalyzer是数据源头，那它推送数据到DiagnosticEngine的具体方式是什么？是直接写入还是通过某个中间件？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "LabAnalyzer通过push操作把原始数据送到Inbox，也就是DiagnosticEngine的收件箱模块。这是第一步。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Agents",
        "Inbox"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画出了LabAnalyzer到Inbox的push连接。接下来Inbox的数据怎么处理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Inbox"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Inbox的数据要经过分类脚本classify-inbox.mjs处理，变成结构化的PatientRecords。这一步很关键，把原始检测数据转换成患者记录格式。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Inbox",
        "Classified"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下，classify-inbox.mjs是Inbox到PatientRecords之间的处理脚本，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Inbox",
        "Classified"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是这个流程。另外LabAnalyzer还有一个manifest文件，需要通过agent-bus.mjs同步到GitHubIssue，也就是EMR_Sync模块，用于追踪检测任务的状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AgentsManifest",
        "GitHubIssue"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加agent-bus.mjs连接。我注意到LabAnalyzer还有RepoScan功能，这个和前面的流程是什么关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RepoScan"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "RepoScan是LabAnalyzer的代码扫描模块，它会输出到ToolsDir，也就是DiagnosticEngine的工具目录。这里没有具体的脚本名称，就是直接的目录映射关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RepoScan",
        "ToolsDir"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。那ToolsDir和之前提到的Classified数据，最终都流向哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ToolsDir",
        "Classified"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Classified数据通过build-insights.mjs生成Insights，也就是DiagnosticEngine的分析洞察模块。而ToolsDir和Insights最终都会通过Astro Build生成Site。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Classified",
        "Insights",
        "ToolsDir",
        "Site"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加build-insights.mjs和两条Astro Build连线。Site是EMR_Sync的站点模块，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Site"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，Site是EMR_Sync的静态站点。它最后要部署到GitHubPages，也就是HIPAA Vault的安全存储。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Site",
        "GitHubPages"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，我加上deploy到GitHubPages的连接。不过我发现整个流程的触发机制还没体现——这些脚本是什么时候运行的？",
