      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好问题。GitHubActions作为DiagnosticEngine的CI/CD模块，会统一调度运行多个脚本：RepoScan、ClassifyScript、InsightsScript，还有AgentBusScript。",
